<p><strong>Health Savings Accounts (HSAs)</strong></p>

<p>HealthyPrice is an excellent option for you to use your IRS qualified Health Savings Account (HSA).  If you have a Health Savings Account (HSA) or a qualified HSA High Deductible Health Plan (HSA-HDHP), then qualified healthcare services and procedures can be purchased at HealthyPrice and reimbursed by your HSA account or plan.</p>

<p>A Health Savings Account (HSA) is an account that you can put money into for current and future medical expenses.  There are certain advantages to putting money into these accounts, including favorable tax treatment.  For more information about your Health Savings Account, or setting up a Health Savings Account, please visit the <a target="_blank" href="http://www.ustreas.gov/offices/public-affairs/hsa/">IRSâ€™ website on Health Savings Accounts</a>. or <a target="_blank" href="/download/IRS_Brochure_HSA-Tri-fold-english-09.pdf">click here for an IRS brochure on Health Savings Accounts</a>.</p>

